  <brief_title>Antiresorptive Effects of a 6-m Treatment Course With Ibandronate Plus Supplementation of Vitamine D and Calcium in Central America</brief_title>
  <official_title>Antiresorptive Effects of a 6-m Treatment Course With Ibandronate Plus Supplementation of Vitamine D and Calcium in Central America</official_title>
