  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Ibandronate is a third-generation biphosphonate with recognized antiresorptive efficacy by
      several international, randomized, double-blind, controlled trials. These studies have not
      included patients from central america, to the best of our knowledge. Therefore, this
      open-label, uncontrolled study, was set out to assess the clinical effects of a 6-m treatment
      course with Ibandronate plus vitamine D and Calcium on bone mineral density and
      health-related quality of life.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
